---
title: Mustard Chicken & Caramelised Pear Salad with Ciabatta Croutons
description: A delicious caramelised pear salad is hearty enough for dinner but light enough for the warmer weather. Add sweet mustard chicken and you’ve got yourself the ultimate weeknight meal. You can thank us later!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5bf49fb6ae08b56add4390b3-fcaee15d.jpg
